<p class='rubric'>{% trans into lang %}Prayer of the day:{% endtrans %} Clare of Assisi</p>
<p class='boilerplate'>
  {% trans into lang %}Lord God,
in the holiness of blessed Clare
you have given a clear light to shine in the darkness of the world.
Give us grace to follow her footsteps,
that we may at last rejoice with her
in the clear light of your eternal glory;
through Jesus Christ our Lord.{% endtrans %}
  {% trans into lang %}Amen{% endtrans %}
</p>